		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://splash247.com/?p=235416</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[<p>The US Treasury has issued a narrowly targeted, 30‑day sanctions waiver allowing Indian refiners to accept Russian‑origin crude and petroleum cargoes already loaded aboard tankers by way of helping fill the gap left by the ongoing war between Iran and the US/Israeli coaliton, which has paralysed hundreds of tankers in the Middle East. The waiver &#8230;</p>
</p>
]]></description>
		
