					<description><![CDATA[<p>The port of Long Beach this week debuted Soleil the Sea Lion Explores the Green Port, a children’s book, penned by Art Marroquin, the port’s media relations manager, with illustrations from San Jose-based Michelle Dinh. Coinciding with Read Across America Week, the book was launched during an assembly held at Birney Elementary School in Long &#8230;</p>
